{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/explore.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>After surviving a crash landing, you awake stranded and lacking abilities or memory. However, a mysterious voice named Root calls out, offering helpful guidance. But be warned, this strange planet is full of killer robots and dangerous obstacles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/piroot_pyramid2.gif?t=1710392493\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/roll.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>Initially limited to rolling based movement, you will soon acquire new abilities and weapons allowing access to more areas, eventually uncovering the world\u2019s many secrets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/piroot51.gif?t=1710392493\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/immersive.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>The engaging story is delivered as a continuous experience without any pauses or overwhelming players with excessive reading.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/piroot22.gif?t=1710392493\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/old.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>Retro inspired pixel art is elevated with dynamic lights and shadows to create a unique visual style. Procedural algorithms give an organic feel to the environment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/piroot13.gif?t=1710392493\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/art.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>As a solo developer's passion project, Piroot is not just a game, it's a labor of love. The custom engine is also open source and includes a level editor, so players can create and share their own stories.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/piroot50.gif?t=1710392493\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/crash.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>Embark on an adventure like no other in Piroot, where boundaries are shattered and the secrets of an entire planet are yours to discover!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Piroot Features...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully explorable planet<br></li><li>Physics based gameplay<br></li><li>Engaging combat <br></li><li>Dynamic lighting<br></li><li>Immersive narrative<br></li><li>Customizable upgrades<br></li><li>Integrated level editor</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2523510?t=1710392493","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1710392493","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1710392493","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1710392493","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523510/extras/explore.png?t=1710392493\" /><br><br>After surviving a crash landing, you awake stranded